{"tid":1236474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【選民】就算登記咗，都要check真啲啊！","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:29:12.000Z","uid":45979,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3272202830972f3ef5f2a9e32cdf4cd6e9b6326e","tid":1236474,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"就算大家遞過form登記做選民，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">都要check清楚自己資格啊！</span></span><br />\nShare條link畀大家，入返個人資料就可以查閱自己嘅選民資格了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZClEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4187a2e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/welcome.jsp</a><br />\n好似我之前唔係屎忽痕去查，都唔知自己同其他市民唔同，冇咗超級區議會選區張票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRBcHiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRBcHiu.png&h=f5de612b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未登記嘅，即刻登記做選民，唔好等啦<br />\n<em><ins><strong>畀埋份form大家download，一次自動有兩票</strong></ins></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZClEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=bc916503\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2ZebeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2ZebeO.jpg&h=498b3553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最老土但係最真嗰句：Your Vote Matters！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d0d76ab3c1854f02bfac059384ebeffdd30e654d","tid":1236474,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7220a3336b4833ef75a21ac28f2beb